
## Assignment Overview

This project is a Spring Boot-based JWT Authentication & Authorization System developed to demonstrate Spring Security, JWT Token-Based Authentication, Role-Based Access Control (RBAC), Exception Handling, Validation, and MySQL database integration.

## Technologies Used

* Java 17
* Spring Boot 3
* Spring Security
* JWT (JSON Web Token)
* Spring Data JPA
* MySQL Database
* Hibernate ORM
* Lombok
* Jakarta Validation
* Maven
* Postman
* Git & GitHub

## Features Implemented

### Authentication Management

* User Registration
* User Login
* JWT Token Generation
* JWT Token Validation

### Authorization Management

* Role-Based Access Control (USER, ADMIN)
* Protected API Endpoints
* Secure Access Using JWT Tokens

### User Management

* Store users in MySQL Database
* Password Encryption using BCrypt
* User Authentication using Spring Security

### Security Features

* Stateless Authentication
* JWT Authentication Filter
* Custom Security Configuration
* Secure Endpoint Access

### Exception Handling

* Global Exception Handling
* Invalid Credentials Handling
* Access Denied Handling
* JWT Expired Token Handling
* Validation Error Handling

