## Authentication Flow

1. Register a new user.

2. Login using registered credentials.

3. Receive JWT token.

4. Add token in Authorization Header:

   ```
   Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>
   ```

5. Access protected endpoints.

6. Role-based authorization controls endpoint access.

